    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited for someone looking for a dedicated restoration project or a source of spare parts. The engine has significant trouble starting and struggles to maintain an idle, likely requiring a major overhaul. The body shows visible rust and significant paint peeling, and the interior has seen better days with torn upholstery and some non-functional electronics. Please note that this car will likely need to be towed from its current location, as it is not currently roadworthy.",
