    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a distinguished example of automotive excellence, this vehicle has been curated to meet rigorous standards of mechanical performance and aesthetic preservation. It features a robust powertrain and a meticulously maintained interior, ensuring a refined driving experience for the sophisticated professional. This unit represents an exceptional opportunity to acquire a well-preserved vehicle that balances luxury with enduring reliability.",
      "price": 34800.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 23
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty car. It\u2019s been such a reliable ride and is still in really solid shape after being well-loved and maintained over the years. It drives beautifully and is perfect for anyone needing a dependable set of wheels for daily commutes or fun road trips! I'm sad to see it go, but I'm excited for it to start its next chapter with you. Drop me a message if you'd like to take it for a spin!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 23
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically sound E92 M3, a quintessential driver\u2019s car powered by the legendary S65 4.0L V8. This high-revving, naturally aspirated unit features individual throttle bodies and an 8,400 RPM redline, paired with a tactile 6-speed manual transmission. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from the M-Variable differential and Electronic Damping Control (EDC) for precise lateral dynamics. Crucial preventative maintenance has been performed, including rod bearing replacement and updated throttle actuators, ensuring the internal reciprocating assembly remains within spec. While the exterior exhibits minor stone chips and patina consistent with a well-enjoyed performance vehicle, the structural integrity and drivetrain performance are excellent. Ideal for the enthusiast seeking a visceral, analog experience without the premium of a collector-grade garage queen.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 23
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Used vehicle. Good condition. Well-maintained engine. Clean interior. Service records available.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 23
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic balance of performance and practicality, having been meticulously maintained throughout its life. The exterior paint holds a deep, impressive shine, though you will find a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear passenger wheel arch\u2014typical signs of a car that has been enjoyed on the open road. Inside, the leather interior is in excellent shape, showing only light softening on the driver\u2019s seat bolster and no cracks or stains. Every feature, from the heated seats to the premium audio system, operates exactly as intended. Mechanically, the car is robust; the engine pulls smoothly, and the transmission shifts are crisp and certain. I have a complete service history available, including a recent fluid flush and a fresh set of tires with plenty of tread remaining. This is a reliable, honest car that is ready for its next chapter without needing immediate investment.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 23
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
