      "description": "We are pleased to present this meticulously maintained vehicle, which exemplifies a harmonious balance of performance and sustained value. This unit has undergone a rigorous multi-point inspection to ensure it meets our dealership's authoritative standards for mechanical reliability and aesthetic presentation. It represents an ideal acquisition for the discerning driver seeking a sophisticated, road-ready vehicle that has been preserved with professional care. We invite you to evaluate this exceptional offering, which stands as a testament to quality engineering and responsible ownership.",
      "price": 34900.0,
